ACERTUS  Trademark Information
 BEACON INVESTMENT ADVISORY SERVICES, INC.
Financial advisory and consultancy services; financial asset management; financial planning; financial planning and investment advisory services; financial planning, namely, developing compensation and benefit packages for corporate executives




Perfect for these industries

Insurance & Financial Services





Words that describe this mark
financial   advisory   consultancy   services   financial   asset   management   financial   planning   financial   planning   investment   advisory   services   financial   planning         developing   compensation   benefit   packages   corporate   executives    
                                    




This is a brand page for the ACERTUS trademark by BEACON INVESTMENT ADVISORY SERVICES, INC. 
                                in MORRISTOWN, NJ, 07960.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this ACERTUS trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner BEACON INVESTMENT ADVISORY SERVICES, INC. of the ACERTUS trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the ACERTUS trademark.
                           






On Thursday, February 21, 2013,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        ACERTUS by 
                        BEACON INVESTMENT ADVISORY SERVICES, INC., MORRISTOWN, NJ  07960.
                        The USPTO has given the ACERTUS 
                        trademark serial  number of  85856435.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for ACERTUS is 
                        
                        
                                            Rachelle A. Dubow, Esq. of 
                                            Morgan, Lewis & Bockius LLP,  1 Federal Street, Boston MA 02110 
                                .
                            The ACERTUS trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for ACERTUS 
                            is Financial advisory and consultancy services; financial asset management; financial planning; financial planning and investment advisory services; financial planning, namely, developing compensation and benefit packages for corporate executives. 
                            





